<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CONTENT id="_3793173_1"><TITLE value="Classroom task"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;p&gt;Form into 6 groups and present Powerpoints on the 2 new dimensions of&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt; the McCumber Cube:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3 x States of Data&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;and 3 x Security Countermeasures&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;img alt="Image result for mccumber cube" src="https://d3i71xaburhd42.cloudfront.net/46bf9dd6df581bc0e75bc1a8e0228143042c33d4/2-Figure1-1.png" width="394" height="417"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Privacy vs Confidentiality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Discuss the differences from a legal standpoint&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;(Cisco course 2.2.1.4)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Image result for privacy vs confidentiality" src="https://securitytoday.com/-/media/SEC/Security-Products/Images/2014/05/Mcafee_Privacy_Security_Confidential_McAfee_large2.jpg" width="437" height="310"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What is meant by the &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 Nines&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Image result for 5 nines" src="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Gary_Weckman/publication/221056071/figure/tbl1/AS:669127739981829@1536543893512/MTTF-MTR-combinations-producing-five-nines.png" width="431" height="170"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With a partner complete Cisco &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Activity 2.2.3.4 and 2.4.3.5&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;nbsp;Share and discuss.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Read 2.5.1.2 ISO domains and as a class, complete&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt; activity 2.5.1.5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Investigate the following &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;professional organisations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; and identify how they might assist you in your studies and/or future careers:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CERT&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;www.cert.org&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SANS&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;www.sans.org&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;MITRE&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; www.mitre.org&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ISC2&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;www.isc2.org&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;NIST&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; www.nist.gov&lt;/p&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
   value="H"/></BODY><DATES><CREATED value="2023-07-24 13:40:45 AWST"/><UPDATED value="2025-04-07 09:43:20 AWST"/><START
